hjb.msg
Class AttributeCopierAssistant

java.lang.Object
  hjb.msg.AttributeCopierAssistant
public class AttributeCopierAssistant
extends Object

AttributeCopierAssistant is to used convert values that are attributes of the JMS Message to encoded HJB values and vice versa.

It contains methods principally used by AttributeCopier and NamedPropertyCopier

Author:
Tim Emiola
See Also:
AttributeCopier,
